name: Dodoco's Whirly Gig
description: A spinning ride best enjoyed with two passengers, this attraction is sponsored by none other than the great mage herself.\n"Come ride on a soft and furry Dodoco, and embark on an unforgettable adventure!"\nThe spinning Dodoco may come to a stop eventually, but for you and the one who rode beside you, there will always be another journey waiting to begin...
